# Unit 2 - Task 02

## Aim
Update the Ubuntu container, install Apache and PHP, commit the changes to a new Docker image, compare the image size with the base image, and push the updated image to Docker Hub.

## Commands

docker run -it --name ubuntu-apache-php ubuntu:latest bash

apt update

apt install apache2 php -y

apache2 -v

php -v

exit

docker commit ubuntu-apache-php dishatribedy/ubuntu-apache-php:v1

docker images

docker push dishatribedy/ubuntu-apache-php:v1

